{
  "stem": "16214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she loved me very much and he loved me very much, and also my older brother, who was quite older than me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's a shame, but I just-- I wish I would be able to find him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as I've mentioned to you, I just received, about three months ago or two months ago-- I received a letter from Warsaw, where I send a letter through the consulate here.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I got-- I got addresses where I should write to for people who are lost, etc.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they just told me that there are 50 people of the same name, and they cannot help me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] Other than that about my other father, the interesting point is that when he was caught by the Polish government and placed in prison, he stayed there for approximately six years or so.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't exactly remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But his wife divorced him during the time when he was in prison.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I guess she didn't want to have anything to do with him because of his association.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she divorced him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he didn't really have not any money, not any place to go to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember him coming to Krosniewice right after he was let out of the jail.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he stayed with us and with his new girlfriend at the time, or maybe wife already.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They stayed with us for several days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember how happy he was to see me and my parents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was so thankful to my parents for the help they-- they gave him, because my father helped him to find a job and gave him money.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he kissed and hugged my mother and my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, I guess Jews are very nice, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
